<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Scanner un code</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/bootstrap.min.css">
</head>
<body class="container py-4">
  <h1 class="mb-2">Scanner un code</h1>
  <p class="text-muted">Autorise l’accès à la caméra puis place le QR-code ou le code-barres dans le cadre. Tu peux aussi saisir le code manuellement si besoin.</p>

  <div id="scan-error" class="alert alert-danger" style="display:none"></div>

  <div class="mb-3 d-flex flex-wrap gap-2">
    <button id="btn-start-scan" class="btn btn-primary">Démarrer le scan</button>
    <button id="btn-stop-scan" class="btn btn-outline-secondary">Arrêter le scan</button>
  </div>

  <video id="preview" style="width:100%;max-width:520px;border-radius:10px;background:#000" muted playsinline></video>

  <form id="manualScanForm" action="/scan/resolve" method="POST" class="mt-3" autocomplete="off">
    <% if (typeof csrfToken === 'function' || csrfToken) { %>
      <input type="hidden" name="_csrf" value="<%= typeof csrfToken === 'function' ? csrfToken() : csrfToken %>">
    <% } %>
    <div class="input-group">
      <input id="manualCode" name="code" class="form-control" placeholder="Saisir un code manuellement" value="<%= code %>">
      <button class="btn btn-success" type="submit">Valider</button>
    </div>
  </form>

  <script src="/vendor/zxing/library.min.js"></script>
  <script src="/vendor/zxing/index.umd.min.js"></script>
  <script src="/js/scanner.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
